course_title: Advanced Open Studio - ADV OPEN STUDIO

001.comments: If registration for VISA 401C 001 is blocked, the course is full and you should register on the corresponding waitlist VISA 401C 01W.

01W.comments: VISA 401C 01W is the waitlist for VISA 401C 001. Students will be moved off the waitlist into the class as seats become available and then notified of their registration via email. Note that registering on the waitlist does not guarantee you a seat in the course.

description: Research-based studio with thematic or disciplinary focus.  Intended for senior Visual Art undergraduate students.
